<template><ModulePageShell title="运营分析" description="科室与手术间统计和病例穿透共用完整病例快照"><template #toolbar><a-button :loading="loading" @click="reload">刷新</a-button></template><template #stats><MetricCard label="病例总数" :value="report?.scope.total ?? 0" icon="IconCalendar"/><MetricCard label="已完成" :value="report?.scope.completed ?? 0" icon="IconCheckCircle"/><MetricCard label="完成率" :value="`${report?.scope.completionRate ?? 0}%`" icon="IconDashboard"/><MetricCard label="缺陷病例" :value="defectCases" icon="IconExclamationCircle" variant="warn"/></template><a-alert v-if="error" type="error" show-icon>{{error}}</a-alert><a-empty v-else-if="!loading&&!report?.scope.total" description="当前范围无真实运营病例"/><a-card v-else class="section-card" :bordered="false" title="手术运营统计"><a-table :data="rows" row-key="key" :pagination="false"><template #columns><a-table-column title="维度" data-index="dimension"/><a-table-column title="名称" data-index="name"/><a-table-column title="台数" data-index="count"/><a-table-column title="占比"><template #cell="{record}">{{record.rate}}%</template></a-table-column></template></a-table></a-card></ModulePageShell></template>
<script setup lang="ts">import{computed,onMounted,ref}from'vue';import MetricCard from'@/components/MetricCard.vue';import ModulePageShell from'@/components/shared/ModulePageShell.vue';import{loadOperationalReport}from'@/services/quality/qualityOperationalReportService';import type{OperationalReportApi}from'@/api/quality';const report=ref<OperationalReportApi|null>(null),loading=ref(false),error=ref('');const rows=computed(()=>[...(report.value?.operations.departments??[]).map(x=>({...x,key:`department-${x.name}`,dimension:'科室'})),...(report.value?.operations.rooms??[]).map(x=>({...x,key:`room-${x.name}`,dimension:'手术间'}))]);const defectCases=computed(()=>report.value?.drilldown.filter(x=>x.defectCount>0).length??0);async function reload(){loading.value=true;error.value='';try{report.value=await loadOperationalReport();}catch(e){report.value=null;error.value=`加载失败：${(e as Error).message}`;}finally{loading.value=false;}}onMounted(reload);</script>
